<a href="http://backgroundrb.rubyforge.org/">backgroundrb(rubyforge)</a><br/>
<a href="https://github.com/gnufied/backgroundrb">backgroundrb(github)</a></p>

<p>以下这个是对backgroundrb在rails3下面的支持<br/>
